how to  
    expand
        subtree                                ⌘→
        all                                    ⌥⌘→
    collapse 
        subtree                                ⌘←           
        all                                    ⌥⌘←
        
    speed up scrolling
        x10                                    ⌘
        x100                                   ⌥
        x1000                                  ^
        
    switch between bright/dark theme           ⌘I
    
    activate search for
        key paths                              ⌘F
        values                                 ⌘G
        
    clear the search                       
                                               ⌘K 
                                               Esc (when search has focus)
                                               
    switch focus from search to tree           ↓ or Tab      
    
    find by path
        all "foo" leaves                       **.foo     
        all "foo" or "bla" leaves              **.foo|bla
        all "foo" leaves below "bar" objects   bar.**.foo
        all "foo" items on level 4             *.*.*.foo    
        all items on level 3                   *.*.*
        first 50 array items                   array.[1-4]?\d
        
    find values
        bool                                   true|false
        int                                    \d+
        float                                  \d+.\d+
        number                                 \d+(.\d+)?
        urls                                   https?://**
